replyContent:
Your problem may be due to the cache memory being too high.
To solve it: 
Go to the Settings of your Android smartphone 
Then go to Applications Choose the "Pango Storytime" application
Go to Storage 
Click on Clear Storage and clear cache 
Restart the application

however, you may lose your saved maps
